[soft guitar]

18:46.647 --> 18:49.345
"King Richard II."
"King Richard III."

18:49.389 --> 18:51.869
"Love's Labour's Lost."
"Macbeth."

18:51.913 --> 18:53.610
"Anthony and Cleo..."
"All's Well that Ends Well."

18:53.654 --> 18:56.265
"Anthony and Cleopatra."
"As You Like It."

18:56.309 --> 18:58.180
"Hamlet."
"Julius Caesar."

18:58.224 --> 19:00.443
"Timon of Athens."
"Titus Andronicus."

19:04.055 --> 19:06.014
"Two Gentlemen in Verona."

19:06.057 --> 19:07.581
"Two Noble Kinsmen."
"Winter's Tale."

19:14.631 --> 19:16.894
- Hi.
- Hi, "28 Summers."

19:16.938 --> 19:18.418
"28 Summers."

19:21.029 --> 19:22.987
Okay, why don't you
back up a little bit,

19:23.031 --> 19:24.511
