19:25.947 --> 19:27.253
- Thanks.
- Thank you. Okay.

19:27.296 --> 19:28.384
- Enjoy it.
- Thank you.

19:28.428 --> 19:29.646
All right.

19:31.996 --> 19:33.998
- Hi.
- Hey, how are ya?

19:36.044 --> 19:38.307
Listen, do you have
