[phone ringing]

27:19.072 --> 27:20.508
Hello, Bookstore.

27:24.164 --> 27:26.645
Can't come in.
Can't come in.

27:26.688 --> 27:28.472
I'm not-- I'm not
letting browsers in.

27:28.516 --> 27:29.909
You can browse
through the window

27:29.952 --> 27:33.303
or on... the website
and choose a book.

27:33.347 --> 27:34.522
Or, if you know a book...

27:39.875 --> 27:41.834
Okay, Suzanne.
I will wrap up the other one

27:41.877 --> 27:43.618
and send it to Cheryl...

27:43.662 --> 27:45.185
- Perfect.
- ...tomorrow, it will go out

27:45.228 --> 27:46.621
maybe tomorrow
or the next day.

27:46.665 --> 27:47.578
- Okay, that's fine.
- Okay?

27:47.622 --> 27:48.928
That's fine, okay.

27:48.971 --> 27:50.364
So you know
what I always do?

27:50.407 --> 27:51.800
I go in...
because I park

27:51.844 --> 27:53.715
in the Loeb's
parking lot...

27:53.759 --> 27:55.195
You feel like you have
to go to Loeb's, right?

27:55.238 --> 27:56.805
So I bought coleslaw.
Would you like it?

27:56.849 --> 27:58.720
- Oh...
- There's a little container

27:58.764 --> 28:00.809
- of coleslaw for you.
- Oh... [laughing]

28:00.853 --> 28:02.768
So I go in there first
and come out.

28:02.811 --> 28:04.378
- You're sweet.
- Okay.

28:04.421 --> 28:05.640
- Thank you.
- So...

28:05.684 --> 28:07.120
So, should I take that?

28:07.163 --> 28:08.687
Because don't
I already have it?

28:08.730 --> 28:09.470
I'll run it through
right now.

28:09.513 --> 28:10.689
Yeah

28:13.213 --> 28:14.562
Suzanne.

28:24.354 --> 28:25.660
Sixteen-ninety-five...

28:25.704 --> 28:28.619
$17, okay.

28:28.663 --> 28:30.230
Oh, God, Matt.
If it ain't one thing,

28:30.273 --> 28:32.623
- it's another, huh?
- It's-- yeah, yeah.

28:32.667 --> 28:35.322
- Yeah.
- So, Saturday.

28:35.365 --> 28:37.019
Saturday, I was here.

28:37.063 --> 28:38.717
Eight customers, you said?

28:38.760 --> 28:40.544
Eight customers.
I told you already.

28:40.588 --> 28:41.807
- [laughing]
- Yeah.

28:41.850 --> 28:43.634
That's a record, isn't it?

28:43.678 --> 28:45.680
- For July, yeah.
