29:05.526 --> 29:07.310
"I was entirely happy.

29:08.964 --> 29:11.924
Perhaps we feel like that
when we die...

29:11.967 --> 29:13.490
and become a part
of something entire.

29:13.534 --> 29:15.754
Whether it is
the sun and air,

29:15.797 --> 29:17.886
or goodness and knowledge.

29:17.930 --> 29:20.584
At any rate,
that is happiness.

29:20.628 --> 29:22.543
That is happiness.
To be dissolved

29:22.586 --> 29:24.719
into something
complete and great."

