29:47.568 --> 29:49.222
it's probably
quite simple, right?

29:49.265 --> 29:53.008
So, um... so...
then what you can do.

29:53.052 --> 29:54.705
One of the first steps
for you to do,

29:54.749 --> 29:57.230
is to get back in touch
with all of our authors

