that we... postponed
all this... past year,

30:00.842 --> 30:03.018
and say,
"Would you be interested

30:03.062 --> 30:06.326
in-- in doing
a Zoom talk?"

30:06.369 --> 30:07.849
There's a thing
in the light of this.

30:07.893 --> 30:09.633
Yeah.

30:09.677 --> 30:11.113
All right,
I got it now, yeah.

30:11.157 --> 30:12.854
So put that in.

