And my dad, one day,
when I was a little kid,

1:03:01.212 --> 1:03:03.823
says, 'Otto, there's somebody
I'd like you to meet.

1:03:03.867 --> 1:03:05.956
It's time you should
meet this guy.'

1:03:05.999 --> 1:03:07.827
And he took me
to the old part of town,

1:03:07.871 --> 1:03:09.524
and there's an old,
wooden sidewalk,

1:03:09.568 --> 1:03:11.483
and there's an old man
leaning a chair up

1:03:11.526 --> 1:03:13.050
against the... wall.

