They-- immediately.

1:06:50.397 --> 1:06:53.966
Within 23 hours,
we met that goal.

1:06:54.010 --> 1:06:55.881
And then it just
kept climbing.

1:06:55.924 --> 1:06:59.493
And then when people said,
"Well, you know...

1:06:59.537 --> 1:07:01.713
raise your goal.
Keep going."

1:07:01.756 --> 1:07:03.758
You-- as I said
in my latest Instagram,

1:07:03.802 --> 1:07:06.892
uh, that
they helped me produce,

